---
title: Tortellini Gratin with Tomato Basil Bolognese and Cheesy Breadcrumbs
description: Don’t let the fancy name fool you. Gratin is just a French way of saying this dish is topped with cheesy breadcrumbs and heated under the broiler until brown and crispy. So it essentially translates to “delicious,” even for the pickiest of eaters. We also snuck some spinach under the crunchy topping for a pop of color and nutrition.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tortellini-gratin-w46-family-08710770.jpg
